/* ais.rc -- embed the application manifest as a resource.
 * id 1   = CREATEPROCESS_MANIFEST_RESOURCE_ID (the manifest for an .exe)
 * type 24 = RT_MANIFEST
 * The manifest turns on comctl32 v6 visual styles (the native themed look,
 * the Win32 equivalent of Swing's System look-and-feel) and asInvoker (no UAC). */
1 24 "ais.manifest"
